<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4290630>
    dc:description "Figure 1. (a–c) Coriotela lasallei n. gen., n. sp. holotype female: (a) Body, dorso-lateral; (b) Head, mesosoma, and anterior part of metasomal, lateral, frl = frenal groove, occ = occipital carina. (c) Fore wing, clv = clava, clavomeres numbered. (d,e) Butiokeras costae n. gen., n. sp. holotype male: (d) Body, dorso-lateral; (e) Body, ventro-lateral." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4290630/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

